1
00:00:02,003 --> 00:00:04,704
Did you bring my power bank?

2
00:00:31,531 --> 00:00:32,664
When I'm with you,

3
00:00:32,665 --> 00:00:34,134
I don't have to worry about a thing.

4
00:00:36,002 --> 00:00:37,242
So, do you want to be together?

5
00:00:38,905 --> 00:00:41,185
In acting, there's the academic way
and the immersive way.

6
00:00:41,574 --> 00:00:43,054
You're definitely the immersive type.

7
00:00:44,477 --> 00:00:46,278
The best part about acting

8
00:00:46,279 --> 00:00:47,679
is when you get so into character

9
00:00:47,680 --> 00:00:49,320
that even you start to believe it's real.

10
00:00:51,051 --> 00:00:52,252
Spoken like a pro.

11
00:00:55,021 --> 00:00:57,790
But look how empty this suitcase is.

12
00:00:57,791 --> 00:00:58,291
Don't you think

13
00:00:58,292 --> 00:00:59,725
we should stuff it with more things?

14
00:00:59,726 --> 00:01:01,427
Make it look a bit messy,

15
00:01:01,428 --> 00:01:02,796
to make it feel more real?

16
00:01:07,133 --> 00:01:08,534
People with messy things

17
00:01:08,535 --> 00:01:10,102
usually feel a bit insecure.

18
00:01:10,103 --> 00:01:12,005
Like that pile of plushies on your bed.

19
00:01:14,874 --> 00:01:18,044
I've got no one to sleep with
so those plushies are all I've got.

20
00:01:27,821 --> 00:01:29,221
Wait, where'd you get this?

21
00:01:29,222 --> 00:01:30,824
You like it? It's custom-made.

22
00:01:32,625 --> 00:01:33,726
Oh my god, I'm so touched.

23
00:01:34,394 --> 00:01:34,961
Consider this

24
00:01:34,962 --> 00:01:36,830
a little gift for our collaboration.

25
00:01:38,264 --> 00:01:39,304
I'm looking forward to it.

26
00:01:40,600 --> 00:01:42,202
I wasn't nearly as thoughtful as you.

27
00:01:42,936 --> 00:01:44,856
But I don't have anything
to give you in return.

28
00:01:45,472 --> 00:01:46,472
Just having you here

29
00:01:47,073 --> 00:01:48,073
is enough.

30
00:01:54,981 --> 00:01:56,181
If I'd known, I would've brought

31
00:01:56,182 --> 00:01:57,382
the one you gave me to cuddle.

32
00:01:58,118 --> 00:01:59,118
You don't need to.

33
00:01:59,786 --> 00:02:00,786
And why's that?

34
00:02:01,020 --> 00:02:02,989
Because you can just cuddle with me.

35
00:02:04,557 --> 00:02:05,425
Keep flirting, why don't you?

36
00:02:05,425 --> 00:02:06,326
I'm going to have to learn

37
00:02:06,327 --> 00:02:07,647
all these little tricks of yours.

38
00:02:08,294 --> 00:02:09,596
It's not a trick.

39
00:02:13,600 --> 00:02:14,701
If you keep this up,

40
00:02:15,602 --> 00:02:17,202
I'm going to start taking you seriously.
